Murray will be keen to put a difficult year behind him and play himself into form ahead of the opening Grand Slam of the season.

After this low-key tournament, Murray represents GB with Heather Watson at the Hopman Cup in Perth, and then it is straight into the Australian Open, an event where he has an admirably consistent record.

